  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study evaluates the effect of ivabradine on endothelial function in patients with
      coronary artery disease (CAD) after complete revascularization with percutaneous coronary
      angioplasty (PCI). At least 30 days after PCI, patients will be randomized to receive
      ivabradine 5 mg twice daily or to continue with standard medical therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
