  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  history of stable coronary disease

          -  complete coronary revascularization with PCI at least 1 month prior to recruitment

          -  sinus rhythm

          -  absence of anginal symptoms

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  resting heart rate &lt;60 beats per minute

          -  severe reduction of left ventricle ejection fraction (&lt;40%)

          -  coronary artery by-pass surgery

          -  myocardial infarction, stroke or cerebral transient ischemic attack within the
             previous 6 months

          -  implanted pacemaker, cardioverter, or defibrillator

          -  sick sinus syndrome

          -  sinoatrial block

          -  congenital long QT

          -  complete atrioventricular block
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
